{"word":"G3563 - νοῦς - noûs - nooce - Mind","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νοῦς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>noûs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>nooce"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Mind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அறிந்துக் கொள்ளுதல், மனது, சிந்தை, கருத்து, எண்ணம், புத்தி, உணர்தல், உள்ளம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"mind, thought, reason; attitude, intention, purpose; understanding, discernment"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the base of <a href=\"#/G1097 - γινώσκω - ginṓskō - ghin-oce'-ko/1097\">G1097</a>; the <i>intellect</i>, that is, <i>mind</i> (divine or human; in thought, feeling, or will); by implication <i>meaning</i>: - mind, understanding. Compare <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1270 - διανόημα - dianóēma - dee-an-o'-ay-mah/1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271 - διάνοια - diánoia - dee-an'-oy-ah/1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425 - δυσνόητος - dysnóētos - doos-no'-ay-tos/1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771 - ἔννοια - énnoia - en'-noy-ah/1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132 - εὐνοέω - eunoéō - yoo-no-eh'-o/2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133 - εὔνοια - eúnoia - yoo'-noy-ah/2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657 - κατανοέω - katanoéō - kat-an-o-eh'-o/2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279 - ἀμετανόητος - ametanóētos - am-et-an-o'-ay-tos/279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340 - μετανοέω - metanoéō - met-an-o-eh'-o/3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539 - νοιέω - noiéō - noy-eh'-o/3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540 - νόημα - nóēma - no'-ay-mah/3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559 - νουθεσία - nouthesía - noo-thes-ee'-ah/3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3562 - νουνεχῶς - nounechōs - noon-ekh-oce'/3562\">G3562</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563 - νοῦς - noûs - nooce/3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306 - προνοέω - pronoéō - pron-o-eh'-o/4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307 - πρόνοια - prónoia - pron'-oy-ah/4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453 - ἀνόητος - anóētos - an-o'-ay-tos/453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454 - ἄνοια - ánoia - an'-oy-ah/454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282 - ὑπονοέω - hyponoéō - hoop-on-o-eh'-o/5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283 - ὑπόνοια - hypónoia - hoop-on'-oy-ah/5283\">G5283</a>"}]}